She looked at Ramulus. She blinked for a moment, like coming out of a 
daydream.  "Hmm?  Oh, sorry.  I lost my place for a moment.  Forgive 
me.  Please, lead me to your CR."  She walked up to him. "And I wish 
to thank you for all your help today.  I'm am very gratefull to you."
